description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 28, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 140, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80285-15474-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [140 Votes, Top 15% Score]
